==English==

===Etymology===
Xmas is an abbreviation for [[Christmas]]. It is derived from the word [[Χριστος]], transliterated as Christos, which is Greek for [[Christ]].  See [[w:Xmas|Wikipedia]] for more discussion.

===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /ˈkrɪsməs/, /ˈeksməs/
*[[SAMPA]]: /"krIsm@s/, /"eksm@s/
*[[AHD]]: /krĭs'məs/, /eks'məs/

